    "Extended Summary": {
      "children": [
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "The function returns the coefficients of the polynomial"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "value": "p(x) = (x - r_0) * (x - r_1) * ... * (x - r_n),"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "in Legendre form, where the "
            },
            {
              "domain": null,
              "role": null,
              "type": "Directive",
              "value": "r_n"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": " are the roots specified in "
            },
            {
              "anchor": null,
              "exists": true,
              "kind": "local",
              "reference": {
                "kind": "local",
                "module": null,
                "path": "roots",
                "type": "RefInfo",
                "version": null
              },
              "type": "Link",
              "value": "roots"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": ". If a zero has multiplicity n, then it must appear in "
            },
            {
              "anchor": null,
              "exists": true,
              "kind": "local",
              "reference": {
                "kind": "local",
                "module": null,
                "path": "roots",
                "type": "RefInfo",
                "version": null
              },
              "type": "Link",
              "value": "roots"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": " n times. For instance, if 2 is a root of multiplicity three and 3 is a root of multiplicity 2, then "
            },
            {
              "anchor": null,
              "exists": true,
              "kind": "local",
              "reference": {
                "kind": "local",
                "module": null,
                "path": "roots",
                "type": "RefInfo",
                "version": null
              },
              "type": "Link",
              "value": "roots"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": " looks something like [2, 2, 2, 3, 3]. The roots can appear in any order."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "If the returned coefficients are "
            },
            {
              "domain": null,
              "role": null,
              "type": "Directive",
              "value": "c"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": ", then"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "value": "p(x) = c_0 + c_1 * L_1(x) + ... +  c_n * L_n(x)"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "The coefficient of the last term is not generally 1 for monic polynomials in Legendre form."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "level": 0,
      "target": null,
      "title": null,
      "type": "Section"
